videos.headline: JuJu Watkins gets the strip and layup
videos.description: USC's JuJu Watkins strips the ball away from the defender, then she finishes the play with a transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (JuJu Watkins gets the strip and layup) 2024/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: JuJu Watkins scores the layup after going backdoor
videos.description: USC's Kayla Padilla makes a nice pass to a cutting JuJu Watkins, who scores the layup.
